statements: SELECT * FROM PerformanceMetrics;
SELECT model_name, accuracy FROM PerformanceMetrics WHERE precision > 0.8;
SELECT id, model_name, f1_score FROM PerformanceMetrics ORDER BY accuracy DESC;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_models FROM PerformanceMetrics;

SELECT model_name, accuracy * precision AS score FROM PerformanceMetrics WHERE recall < 0.7 ORDER BY score
SELECT * FROM model_performance_metrics;
